text: Tried this pizza for the first time about a month and a half ago, been there 4 times since.  This flavored stuffed crust satisfies every taste bud my mouth has to offer.  It even kept my kid quiet for a whopping 11 minutes. I've been eating …More

name: Jasmin Gutierrez
text: I always order from this store and the white lane store. All employees have been super nice each time I’ve order. Chris, however, has been the nicest and kindest person I’ve order pizza from at this location. Whenever I call, I like to ask for him because I know he will take care of us! Keep up the good work chris.

name: Wonder Woman Nerd
text: Not only the best of the inexpensive pizzas, but really good pizza. The flavored crust is awesome. I usually get the pizza delux sub brushed with garlic crust flavoring.

name: Cindy Denise Horton
text: Walked in and placed my order for a personal pizza and a drink. Paid cash. She told me it would be about 15 minutes. When 15 minutes was up I still didn’t have my pizza. Upon asking they told me it would be about 30 more minutes. What!!! …More

name: Kai Fox
text: I called and order the pizza they said it would be ready in thirty minutes. So i went and picked it up and i got home to open my box of pizza and it was cold to the touch. I would not recommend it.

name: James Berryhill
text: We ordered a pepperoni extra cheese, got a cheese pizza, called and spoke to Chris, not a chance he made a mistake, he did !! First try here, never again !!! He took order so it’s impossible for a mistake !! Look at your rating Chris, good luck, you have 0 customer service skills !!!

name: Karrie Rhodes
text: It was great. Ordered their heart shaped pizza for Valentine's day. Was awesome. Thank you! I did carry out. You guys did amazing, especially for how busy you were. Keep up the good work!

name: JAZMINE VANCE
text: I have ordered from this establishment for over a year and tonight they delivered a pizza that looked like it had flipped over in the Box. However, I contacted Hungry Howie’s and spoke to Nori and she was kind enough to give me credit for another pizza. She had a great attitude and was understanding, which matters to me.
